                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17720909-40-off204 t17720909-40-crimeloc206"></join>. On Tuesday night the 8th of this month when I shut up at night, I missed a silver tankard; it was advertised afterwards by Marks the Jew; I went to his house, and saw the tankard; I never saw the prisoner, to my knowledge, in my life before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17720909-40-person531">
                  David
                   Levi
               <interp inst="t17720909-40-person531" type="surname" value="Levi"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17720909-40-person531" type="given" value="David"></interp>
